{"tid":2415581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"資訊科技辦公室：偽冒「安心出行」情況越趨嚴重 已交警方跟進 市民小心私隱外洩風險切勿以身試法","createTime":"2021-02-20T11:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T12:25:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bd414fc00920f9e54f85a5bbcc976c121da5bf","tid":2415581,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"坊間對「安心出行」的私隱疑慮未除，早前有網民製作「翻版」網站，用戶只要自行輸入地點就可以假扮已掃瞄「安心出行」。政府資訊科技總監辦公室今日（20 日）表示，偽冒「安心出行」的情況越趨嚴重，指由於製造或使用有關偽冒程式有可能觸犯相關法例，資科辦已將所有懷疑偽冒網站及流動應用程式交由警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n資科辦又提醒，登入或使用來歷不明的網站或應用程式，會構成網絡安全及私隱外洩風險，市民應做好資訊保安，切勿以身試法。"},{"pid":"7fb8b54f17356cdfee5e21600ec27f3e08588293","tid":2415581,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d512551afd7769340e8ac8e5d852979bc51a8217","tid":2415581,"uid":185349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"有冇外國link板"},{"pid":"9ebae1fd10c7051310b65255af4803e73d887a54","tid":2415581,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0f730970c1994decebf15aac930680c00dbc1b","tid":2415581,"uid":113250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:19:15.000Z","msg":"有可能觸犯相關法例<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人仲驚呢句咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd684e7a8378e95df9915525f7a1c762dedf4f6","tid":2415581,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"資科辦又提醒，登入或使用來歷不明的網站或應用程式，會構成網絡安全及私隱外洩風險<br />\n<br />\n<br />